pageContent.title: Sustainability Trips
pageContent.subtitle: Sustainable Innovations Awaits You
pageContent.content: Experience hands-on learning beyond the classroom through real-world sustainability challenges. Learn more about SUTD's  First Sustainability Trip in Spring 2024 to Kyoto, Japan. Gain insights from a country with mature sustainability practices, exploring evolving policies, cultural traditions, and success stories. Prepare to become a technically grounded innovator capable of contributing to a sustainable future.
